race.description: Wagga Wagga City Council Mdn Hcp
race.comment: CARRY ON LIZZY (2) stuck on well fresh to finish second last start over 1400m at Cootamundra. Is sure to have come on with that run under her belt and finds a very thin maiden. Perfectly placed to get off the mark. EXTRA HANDS (5) finished full of running and found the line nicely in the same maiden to grab third at Cootamundra. BURNING AMBITION (3) will find this company much to his liking and can improve sharply. Draws well and is one of the main hopes. REEF ROAD (7) also comes through the Cootamundra maiden, where he finished fourth, an improvement on his eighth at this track the run before. Has a few ratings littered in his form that suggest he can take this out if he brings his A-game. DOPPIO (4) has shown good early toe of late. He could take some catching if she applies those tactics again over this shorter journey.
